OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy start this morning with
OL,6,Fpatchy rain. Then the rest of the day
OL,7,Fwill see bright or sunny spells and
OL,8,Fscattered showers, occasionally heavy
OL,9,Fthis afternoon. Warmer than of late.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be partly
OL,12,Fcloudy with scattered showers, heavy
OL,13,Fat first. Then the rest of the night
OL,14,Fwill see variable amounts of cloud and
OL,15,Fsome showery rain.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FSome bright or sunny spells
OL,18,Fand a scattering of showers, these
OL,19,Fmainly in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
